    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Ranged Only</strong></p><hr /><p>Your weapon can shoot projectiles that split into simple ropes or nets around your foes' legs to trip your targets, and you can climb using the grappling hooks built into the weapon. Your weapon invention gains the climbing (worth <strong>1 TP</strong>) and ranged trip (worth <strong>3 TP</strong>) traits, as well as the tethered trait if it is thrown. You add the ranged trip trait to the list of traits you can select for ranged multi-tool upgrades, and the climbing trait to the list of traits you can select for melee multi-tool upgrades.</p>",
